snippet.title: Sound & Music I Feature Highlights Ep 12 I Cities: Skylines II
snippet.description:
Shhh... Can you hear that? 🐦 Birds chirping, 🐶 dogs barking, 🚗 tires screeching, 🚅 trains honking? It sounds like Cities: Skylines II to me! 

What goes into making a city sound like a city, and what can a mayor listen to whilst they're building their city? Sound & Music makes for a wonderful listen! 🎧

Footage captured In-Game is not final and might change in time for release.

Pre-Order Cities: Skylines II NOW!
